            "Carbohydrates: Remaining calories after protein and fat (4 kcal per gram) — primary energy source",
            "Example (2,500 kcal diet, 75kg person): 150g protein (600 kcal), 70g fat (630 kcal), 318g carbs (1,270 kcal)",
