            "? — Zero or one occurrence: colou?r matches 'color' and 'colour'",
            "{n} — Exactly n occurrences: \\d{4} matches exactly 4 digits",
            "{n,m} — Between n and m occurrences: \\d{2,4} matches 2 to 4 digits",
